<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.5.1">
<l>tantai kālil peruvilaṅku tāḷa viḻa naḷḷiruṭkaṇ</l>
<l>vanta ventai perumāṉā maruvi niṉṟa vūrpōlum</l>
<l>munti vāṉam maḻaipoḻiyum mūvā vuruvil maṟaiyāḷar</l>
<l>anti mūṉṟu maṉalōmpu maṇiyār vīti yaḻuntūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city where the great lord stands, cherishing the cows, our father</l>
<l rend="indent">who, in the dark of night,</l>
<l>Was born so that the bolts of the great fetters on his father’s feet loosened,</l>
<l>It seems is Aḻuntūr with beautiful streets</l>
<l rend="indent">where Vedic experts of ageless beauty</l>
<l>Maintain the fire three times [a day], and where</l>
<l rend="indent">the skies, rushing, gush rain.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
